Adds a new amplifier to amplifiers structure all coordinates in detector-based coordinates

Parameters:
[in] xstart lower right x position
[in] precols number of predata pixels in x direction (prescans)
[in] datacols number of col data pixels (x direction)
[in] postcols number of postdata pixels in x direction (oversscans)
[in] ystart lower right y position
[in] prerows number of predata lines in y direction (yprescans)
[in] datarows number of row data lines (y direction)
[in] postrows number of postdata lines in y direction (yoversscans)
[in] xdetstart lower right position of detctor in FPA
[in] ydetstart lower right position of detector in FPA
[in] type amplifier type (lowerleft (LL), Lowerright (LR), UpperLeft (UL) or UpperRight (UR
[in] rotate rotation angle for the amplifier (0,90,180 or 270 allowed only)
[in] flip indicates if the amplifier is flipped
[in] extension indicates the extension number where this should be mapped
[in] detno indicates the detector number to which this amplifier belongs
[in] ampno indicates the amplifier number
[in] discard indicates if this amplifier should be discarded
